[
    {
        "content": "<p>Hi folks! :)</p>\n<p>I'm following <span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"414281\">@Wedson Almeida Filho</span>  tutorial here:<br>\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-l-8WrGHEGI?t=4327\">https://youtu.be/-l-8WrGHEGI?t=4327</a></p>\n<p>but it's not registering the scull device for me:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"txt\"><pre><span></span><code>/ # ls /dev/scull*\nls: /dev/scull*: No such file or directory\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Although there was no error  during <code>init</code> and it prints: <code>[    0.582110] scull: Hello world!</code></p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"sd\">//! Scull module in Rust.</span>\n\n<span class=\"k\">use</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">kernel</span>::<span class=\"n\">io_buffer</span>::<span class=\"n\">IoBufferWriter</span><span class=\"p\">;</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"k\">use</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">kernel</span>::<span class=\"n\">prelude</span>::<span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"p\">;</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"k\">use</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">kernel</span>::<span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"n\">file</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">miscdev</span><span class=\"p\">};</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">module</span><span class=\"o\">!</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">type</span>: <span class=\"nc\">Scull</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">name</span>: <span class=\"nc\">b</span><span class=\"s\">\"scull\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">license</span>: <span class=\"nc\">b</span><span class=\"s\">\"GPL\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n\n<span class=\"k\">struct</span> <span class=\"nc\">Scull</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">_dev</span>: <span class=\"nc\">Pin</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"nb\">Box</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">miscdev</span>::<span class=\"n\">Registration</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">Scull</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n\n<span class=\"cp\">#[vtable]</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"k\">impl</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">file</span>::<span class=\"n\">Operations</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">for</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Scull</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">fn</span> <span class=\"nf\">open</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">_context</span>: <span class=\"kp\">&amp;</span><span class=\"p\">(),</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">_file</span>: <span class=\"kp\">&amp;</span><span class=\"nc\">file</span>::<span class=\"n\">File</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-&gt; <span class=\"nb\">Result</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"n\">pr_info</span><span class=\"o\">!</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s\">\"File was opened</span><span class=\"se\">\\n</span><span class=\"s\">\"</span><span class=\"p\">);</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"nb\">Ok</span><span class=\"p\">(())</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"p\">}</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">fn</span> <span class=\"nf\">read</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"n\">_data</span>: <span class=\"p\">(),</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"n\">_file</span>: <span class=\"kp\">&amp;</span><span class=\"nc\">file</span>::<span class=\"n\">File</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"n\">_writer</span>: <span class=\"kp\">&amp;</span><span class=\"nc\">mut</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">impl</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">IoBufferWriter</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"n\">_offset</span>: <span class=\"kt\">u64</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-&gt; <span class=\"nb\">Result</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"kt\">usize</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"n\">pr_info</span><span class=\"o\">!</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s\">\"File was read</span><span class=\"se\">\\n</span><span class=\"s\">\"</span><span class=\"p\">);</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"nb\">Ok</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"p\">}</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n\n<span class=\"k\">impl</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">kernel</span>::<span class=\"n\">Module</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">for</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Scull</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">fn</span> <span class=\"nf\">init</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">_name</span>: <span class=\"kp\">&amp;</span><span class=\"o\">'</span><span class=\"nb\">static</span> <span class=\"nc\">CStr</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">_module</span>: <span class=\"kp\">&amp;</span><span class=\"o\">'</span><span class=\"nb\">static</span> <span class=\"nc\">ThisModule</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-&gt; <span class=\"nb\">Result</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"bp\">Self</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"n\">pr_info</span><span class=\"o\">!</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s\">\"Hello world!</span><span class=\"se\">\\n</span><span class=\"s\">\"</span><span class=\"p\">);</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"kd\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">reg</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">match</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">miscdev</span>::<span class=\"n\">Registration</span>::<span class=\"n\">new_pinned</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">fmt</span><span class=\"o\">!</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s\">\"scull\"</span><span class=\"p\">),</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">())</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"nb\">Err</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">e</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"w\">                </span><span class=\"n\">pr_err</span><span class=\"o\">!</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s\">\"Error registering scull in miscdev: {:?}\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">e</span><span class=\"p\">);</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"w\">                </span><span class=\"fm\">panic!</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s\">\"adios\"</span><span class=\"p\">);</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"p\">},</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"nb\">Ok</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">d</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">d</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"p\">};</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"nb\">Ok</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">Self</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">_dev</span>: <span class=\"nc\">reg</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">})</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"p\">}</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>I guess it's because of the <code>initrd</code> parameter passed to <code>qemu</code></p>\n<p>In the presentation he's using:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Bash\"><pre><span></span><code>qemu-system-x86_64 -nographic -kernel vmlinux -initrd initrd.img -nic user,model<span class=\"o\">=</span>rtl8139,hostfwd<span class=\"o\">=</span>tcp:55555-:23\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>But I'm using:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Bash\"><pre><span></span><code>qemu-system-x86_64 -m 2G -nographic -kernel vmlinux -initrd initramfs.cpio.gz\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>And I created this <code>initramfs</code> file using this tutorial: <a href=\"https://github.com/d0u9/Linux-Device-Driver/blob/bb9c6e9ec67ae4656cc9f2a39bf4fe0f4c2a8859/02_getting_start_with_driver_development/03_build_initramfs.md\">https://github.com/d0u9/Linux-Device-Driver/blob/bb9c6e9ec67ae4656cc9f2a39bf4fe0f4c2a8859/02_getting_start_with_driver_development/03_build_initramfs.md</a></p>",
        "id": 290221003,
        "sender_full_name": "Leandro Coutinho",
        "timestamp": 1658315821
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Do you see <code>scull</code> when you do <code>cat /proc/misc</code>?</p>",
        "id": 290225418,
        "sender_full_name": "Wedson Almeida Filho (Old Google account)",
        "timestamp": 1658318468
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>if you do, the most likely problem is that you don't have devtmpfs mounted in /dev. You can run <code>mount -t devtmpfs none /dev</code> to mount it.</p>",
        "id": 290226395,
        "sender_full_name": "Wedson Almeida Filho (Old Google account)",
        "timestamp": 1658319083
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Also, the <code>initrd.img</code> in the VM comes from <code>~/busybox/_install</code> -- you can run <code>find . | cpio -o -H newc | gzip &gt; ../../linux/initrd.img</code> from that directory to rebuild the image after making changes to it</p>",
        "id": 290226649,
        "sender_full_name": "Wedson Almeida Filho (Old Google account)",
        "timestamp": 1658319243
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"414281\">Wedson Almeida Filho</span> <a href=\"#narrow/stream/291565-Help/topic/.2Fdev.2Fscull*.3A.20No.20such.20file.20or.20directory/near/290225418\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Do you see <code>scull</code> when you do <code>cat /proc/misc</code>?</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>No, but after running <code>mount -t devtmpfs none /dev</code> it worked! :D</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Bash\"><pre><span></span><code>/ <span class=\"c1\"># ls dev</span>\nconsole  null     tty      ttyS0\n/ <span class=\"c1\"># ls proc/</span>\n/ <span class=\"c1\"># cat /proc/misc</span>\ncat: can<span class=\"s1\">'t open '</span>/proc/misc<span class=\"err\">'</span>: No such file or directory\n/ <span class=\"c1\"># ls /dev/scull*</span>\nls: /dev/scull*: No such file or directory\n/ <span class=\"c1\"># mount -t devtmpfs none /dev</span>\n/ <span class=\"c1\"># ls /dev/scull*</span>\n/dev/scull\n/ <span class=\"c1\"># cat /dev/scull</span>\n<span class=\"o\">[</span>   <span class=\"m\">56</span>.335303<span class=\"o\">]</span> scull: File <span class=\"k\">for</span> device <span class=\"m\">0</span> was opened\n<span class=\"o\">[</span>   <span class=\"m\">56</span>.339563<span class=\"o\">]</span> scull: File <span class=\"k\">for</span> device <span class=\"m\">0</span> was <span class=\"nb\">read</span>\n/ <span class=\"c1\"># echo abc &gt; dev/scull</span>\n<span class=\"o\">[</span>  <span class=\"m\">637</span>.601976<span class=\"o\">]</span> scull: File <span class=\"k\">for</span> device <span class=\"m\">0</span> was opened\n<span class=\"o\">[</span>  <span class=\"m\">637</span>.604623<span class=\"o\">]</span> scull: File <span class=\"k\">for</span> device <span class=\"m\">0</span> was written\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Muito obrigado!</p>\n<p>Looking forward to your next sessions! <span aria-label=\"smile\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f642\" role=\"img\" title=\"smile\">:smile:</span></p>",
        "id": 290306010,
        "sender_full_name": "Leandro Coutinho",
        "timestamp": 1658354864
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I was able to write (echo), because I used your latest version:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"sd\">//! Scull module in Rust.</span>\n\n<span class=\"k\">use</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">kernel</span>::<span class=\"n\">io_buffer</span>::<span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"n\">IoBufferReader</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">IoBufferWriter</span><span class=\"p\">};</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"k\">use</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">kernel</span>::<span class=\"n\">prelude</span>::<span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"p\">;</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"k\">use</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">kernel</span>::<span class=\"n\">sync</span>::<span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"n\">smutex</span>::<span class=\"n\">Mutex</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Ref</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">RefBorrow</span><span class=\"p\">};</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"k\">use</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">kernel</span>::<span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"n\">file</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">miscdev</span><span class=\"p\">};</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">module</span><span class=\"o\">!</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">type</span>: <span class=\"nc\">Scull</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">name</span>: <span class=\"nc\">b</span><span class=\"s\">\"scull\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">license</span>: <span class=\"nc\">b</span><span class=\"s\">\"GPL\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n\n<span class=\"k\">struct</span> <span class=\"nc\">Device</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">number</span>: <span class=\"kt\">usize</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">contents</span>: <span class=\"nc\">Mutex</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"nb\">Vec</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"kt\">u8</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n\n<span class=\"k\">struct</span> <span class=\"nc\">Scull</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">_dev</span>: <span class=\"nc\">Pin</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"nb\">Box</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">miscdev</span>::<span class=\"n\">Registration</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">Scull</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n\n<span class=\"cp\">#[vtable]</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"k\">impl</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">file</span>::<span class=\"n\">Operations</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">for</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Scull</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"w\"></span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">type</span> <span class=\"nc\">OpenData</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Ref</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\